Make sure you have gcc, g++ and conda installed. 
Conda can be installed by following the instructions here:
http://conda.pydata.org/docs/install/quick.html#miniconda-quick-install-requirements

To install and switch to the envrionment specified in environment.yml:
../pyri$ conda env create
../pyri$ source activate -n pyri

To build murmurhash:
../pyri$ python setup.py build_ext -b pyri/
